title: Manufacturing of baby strollers, tricycles pillar business in Quzhou County
content: Employees assemble products in Quzhou County, Handan City of north China's Hebei Province, Dec. 15, 2020. Manufacturing of baby strollers and tricycles found its way into Quzhou County in 1970s, and is now a pillar and specialty business with over 1,800 local companies involved in. (Xinhua/Zhu Xudong)
